#. translators: %s: version number.
msgid "Version %s (Den-O)"
msgstr "版本 %s (Den-O)"

msgid "What's New in v3.7 (Den-O)"
msgstr "v3.7 (Den-O) 更新内容"

msgid "Background Jobs:"
msgstr "后台任务："

msgid "Manual, bulk, scheduled, and regenerate flows now queue immediately and run through WP-Cron in the background."
msgstr "手动、批量、定时和重新生成操作现在会立即排队，并通过 WP-Cron 在后台运行。"

msgid "Live Generation Log:"
msgstr "实时生成日志："

msgid "Track queued, running, succeeded, and failed jobs with source, runtime, and clear error reasons."
msgstr "跟踪排队中、运行中、成功和失败的任务，包含来源、运行时间和详细错误原因。"

msgid "Clearer Failures:"
msgstr "更清晰的失败信息："

msgid "Failed jobs now show the actual error message and include a direct report link for support."
msgstr "失败的任务现在会显示实际错误消息，并包含直接反馈链接。"

msgid "Still Your Workflow:"
msgstr "保持你的工作流程："

msgid "Existing draft-first generation, bulk tools, scheduling, and regenerate actions continue to work on top of the new job system."
msgstr "现有的草稿优先生成、批量工具、定时计划和重新生成操作在新的任务系统上继续正常工作。"

msgid "Our Philosophy"
msgstr "我们的理念"

msgid "WP-AutoInsight is built on the belief that you should own your tools and your data. Unlike SaaS platforms that charge high monthly fees and lock your content behind a subscription, this plugin runs on your own infrastructure and uses your own API keys at cost."
msgstr "WP-AutoInsight 的理念是：你应该拥有自己的工具和数据。与收取高额月费、将内容锁在订阅背后的 SaaS 平台不同，这个插件运行在你自己的服务器上，使用你自己的 API 密钥，按量付费。"

msgid "You pay only for what you use, directly to the AI providers, with no markup from us. Your site, your rules, your content."
msgstr "你只需按用量直接向 AI 服务商付费，没有任何加价。你的网站，你的规则，你的内容。"

msgid "Professional Services"
msgstr "专业服务"

msgid "Need help with content strategy or custom AI integrations?"
msgstr "需要内容策略或自定义 AI 集成方面的帮助？"

msgid "Work With Me"
msgstr "与我合作"

msgid "Resources"
msgstr "资源"

msgid "Support Forum"
msgstr "支持论坛"

msgid "Rate the Plugin"
msgstr "为插件评分"

