msgstr "在发布框中点击「转写并创建文章」"

msgid "The AI will transcribe the audio and create a formatted blog post"
msgstr "AI 将转写音频并创建格式化的博客文章"

msgid "Note:"
msgstr "注意："

msgid "Audio files must be under 25MB (OpenAI Whisper limit). Longer files may take several minutes to process."
msgstr "音频文件必须小于 25MB（OpenAI Whisper 限制）。较长的文件可能需要几分钟处理。"

